product.bullet_points:
• OFFICIAL CERTIFICATION BY QUALCOMM: AINOPE is proud to announce its status as a 1% partner of Qualcomm's official certification program. Furthermore, our QC fast car charger, including our Super Car Charger, Samsung S25 Ultra Car Charger and Android Car Charger models, underwent rigorous testing in Qualcomm's approved military-grade laboratory. This testing encompassed fast charging speed, device compatibility, battery health, and charging heat dissipation. Rest assured, AINOPE delivers the same quick charging experience as the original charger, ensuring your devices receive optimal power without compromising safety.
• DUAL PORTS QC3.0 FAST CHARGING: Experience the latest in turbo charging technology with our dual ports QC3.0 fast car charger. Capable of delivering a total output of 45W of power, our chargers enable your devices to charge from 0% to 55% in just 35 minutes. Thanks to the smart dual chip design, both our Samsung S25 Ultra Car Charger and Android Car Charger can simultaneously charge two devices at QC3.0 speed, providing up to 3 times faster charging for compatible devices, including iPhones.
• FULL METAL MINI BODY AND SAFETY GUARANTEE: Our upgraded metal mini USB car charger, available in both Super Car Charger and Android Car Charger variants, boasts a compact 1.79inch*0.94inch body, ensuring durability and safety. Unlike plastic chargers, our metal design dissipates heat efficiently, preventing overheating and burnout. With multiple safety certifications and precautions in place, including protection against over-current and overcharging, our chargers prioritize the safety of your electronics.
• Universal Compatibility: Equipped with intelligent control technology, these chargers deliver maximum power to charge Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra, Android and iPhone16/15/14/13/12 smartphones efficiently.
• FIRM AND UNINTERRUPTED POWER: Designed for reliability, our chargers feature metal shrapnel at the bottom that has undergone rigorous plug-in testing, ensuring a secure connection in your car's lighter socket. Additionally, the snap-on shrapnel connections of our rapid car chargers provide stable and elastic power transmission, even in changing traffic conditions, keeping your smartphone charged without interruption.
• SATISFIED AFTER-SALES SERVICE: Your satisfaction is our priority. If you encounter any issues with our car chargers, please don't hesitate to contact us. Our reliable customer service team is available 24/7 to provide you with the right solution.
